<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hesap360 | Finansal Karar Destek Merkezi</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root { --blue: #0066ff; --text: #1a1a1a; --gray: #f5f7fa; --border: #eef1f6; }
        body { background: #fff; color: var(--text); font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; margin: 0; }
        .container { max-width: 1140px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
        
        nav { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 25px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
        .logo { font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 800; text-decoration: none; color: var(--text); }
        .logo span { color: var(--blue); }

        .hero { text-align: center; padding: 80px 0; }
        .hero h1 { font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -2px; margin: 0; color: #000; }
        .hero p { color: #666; font-size: 1.2rem; margin: 20px 0 40px; }

        .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 30px; }
        .card { 
            background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 40px 30px; border-radius: 24px; 
            text-decoration: none; color: inherit; transition: 0.3s; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
        }
        .card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); border-color: var(--blue); box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,102,255,0.08); }
        .card i { font-size: 2.2rem; color: var(--blue); margin-bottom: 25px; display: block; }
        .card h3 { font-size: 1.25rem; margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-weight: 700; }
        .card p { color: #777; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; }

        footer { margin-top: 100px; padding: 40px 0; background: var(--gray); text-align: center; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .f-links a { color: #666; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 15px; font-weight: 600; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <nav><a href="/" class="logo">HESAP<span>360</span></a></nav>
        <div class="hero">
            <h1>Doğru Hesap. Net Karar.</h1>
            <p>Finansal geleceğinizi profesyonel araçlarla planlayın.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid">
            <a href="/kredi" class="card"><i class="fa-solid fa-coins"></i><h3>Kredi</h3><p>En uygun faizli kredi tekliflerini karşılaştırın.</p></a>
            <a href="/mevduat" class="card"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-dots"></i><h3>Mevduat</h3><p>Birikimleriniz için en yüksek getiriyi bulun.</p></a>
            <a href="/kredi-karti" class="card"><i class="fa-solid fa-credit-card"></i><h3>Kartlar</h3><p>Kredi kartı aidat ve puanlarını inceleyin.</p></a>
            <a href="/kredi-limit" class="card"><i class="fa-solid fa-gauge-high"></i><h3>Limit</h3><p>Çekebileceğiniz kredi miktarını hesaplayın.</p></a>
        </div>
        <footer>
            <div class="f-links">
                <a href="/bilgi/hakkimizda">Hakkımızda</a>
                <a href="/bilgi/kvkk">KVKK</a>
                <a href="/bilgi/iletisim">İletişim</a>
            </div>
            <p style="margin-top:20px;">© 2026 Hesap360. Tüm hakları saklıdır.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
